sellerCard.description: I am a hardworking Software Engineer. I spend lots of my time achieving my goals and improving my development skills. I am passionate about my studies and skills. I specialize in PHP Website Designing & Development, E-Commerce Store, and Laravel Wordpress CodeIgniter, Finding Bugs and issues and optimization of your site. I have Great Experience & Reputation on different Freelance Platforms. Here to provide you Quality Services on Time & an Affordable Price. Consultation is always FREE so contact me to know how I can help you.

description.content:
Are you looking for extreme, versatile front & back-end web developer?


I will develop any scale (small, medium, large) web application or do any web programming. Please contact me with your complete requirements. I can bring your idea / concept in to reality.


  • HTML5 & CSS3

  •  MongoDB

  •  Connect with third party API integrations
  • ASP.Net
  • Python / Django

reviews.comment: Shahbaz is a pleasure to work with. He is knowledge , helpful and goes the extra mile to ensure the work is done. It really important that you can find someone you can trust as there are some sellers who promise much but deliver little. Shahbaz will deliver what he promises and that is a rare quality.

It was really good to have Shahbaz onboard with this project. He has a lot of technical expertise within this field and uses his talents to help the client. You can trust him on any type of job to work with you well and keep you informed of developments.
I had no knowledge of how to do this and he was very understanding and willing to explain. Always responded quickly. Made sure we understood each other. Very professional. Very Kind.
It was nice working with Shahbaz.
